Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa is back, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the opposite seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for us now!\NThey're going to attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?! I thought he said\Nhe wasn't gonna capture us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would we know?!\NHurry up and get ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving this back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on board, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Board my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are total amateurs who\Ncould only manage makeshift repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a pity for such a magnificent ship\Nnot to have a shipwright on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have much choice\Nbut to help you guys out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franky, will be the shipwright on your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Departing the City of Water!\NUsopp Mans Up and Brings Closure to the Duel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the scrap heap island at\Nthe southeast seashore, about to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna head there right away!\NGet on board immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp! We lightheartedly\Nparted with Luffy-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna complain, talk to Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who chewed me out\Nand made me come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How bossy of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's my grandson, so..."\Non the transponder snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Mind your own\Nbusiness, you greenhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Admiral, what about you?\NIs it okay for you to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot of work going back by bike.\NWell, don't worry. I won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... I think that also can be a\Nproblem when facing our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Take good care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Franky Family will live on forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats! You guys take care, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure you don't have to\Nwait for one more person, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did wait. Ever since I heard what Sanji told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried so that our room at\NGalley-La wouldn't be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Usopp is coming back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He was by himself rehearsing\Nhow he'd rejoin us at the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! So he really wants to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go get him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always gotta do things the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow any of us to go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do, don't assume a\Nsubservient attitude towards him, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna accept him\Nuntil he apologizes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro! Why?!\N--Hey! Who are you to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what feelings were involved\Nin Luffy and Usopp's first argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or no matter who the right one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once a man decides to fight a duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the outcome of the duel decides that argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the ship\Nbelongs to you, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, I'll take the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight a duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and walked out on us on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen, you guys. He might be\Nan idiot, but he's still our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Usopp can't treat him with\Nrespect when things are critical,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're better off not having him in our gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a captain stops commanding respect,\Nhis gang will fall apart without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! I don't care if you\Nwant to act happy-go-lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you, the man who is above me,\Never shows weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,next time, the one leaving the gang will be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that won't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that that idiot\Nnow wants to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if he tries to fudge on this issue\Nwithout taking any responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept that no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll leave him on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Zoro. It's true that\Nhis actions weren't appropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can give him a good\Ntalking-to once he comes ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is leaving the gang such a trivial matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this time,\Nwhat he's saying is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can trust a man\Nwho'd do such a thing on impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is what it boils down to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the first words coming from Usopp are\Na sincere apology, then we're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's no place\Nhere for him to come back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not little kids playing pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a new ship and\Nmove on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have several days before the\Nship gets completed and we set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just stay here and wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for him there all this time,\Nbut he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure... he'll have a fun life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't quit being a pirate,\Nso I hope I'll see him some day on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna go back to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a magnificent ship!\NThey're all waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is, how will I rejoin them naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:10:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter how they act,\NI've got 100 strategies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strong candidate for my first\Nwords has to be these, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you're begging me so\Nmuch that you're in tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I can come back if\Nyou make me Vice Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you, Vice Captain Usopp! Yay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll do whatever you tell us, so please\Ncome back." They might say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the very example of a man who\Nturns even his mistakes to good use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this adverse situation, I'll further\Nendear myself to them and live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'd better hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to stay, but goodbye,\NWater Seven, the City of Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, let's wait a little longer.\NWe're not in a rush or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They found us! It's the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vice Admiral Garp's battleship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Straw Hat! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Grandpa! This is Grandpa!\NIf you can hear me, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you weren't gonna capture us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the thing is, a lot\Nhas happened since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm gonna send you\Nto the bottom of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not doing this as an\Napology for that or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll fight your gang all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a cannonball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor... Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! H-He fired a cannonball\Nwith his bare hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That came flying at us with more\Npower than the ones fired by cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he was just throwing a baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power's been declining lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!\NWe're getting out of here for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or our new ship will be blasted to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring 1,000 cannonballs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! A whole bunch of those\Nthings are about to come flying at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Fist Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... Against that,\Nno ship would stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get started, shall we, lads?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you can\Nrun from me! Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!\NWe'll take care of the cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Is he really not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Usopp's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way! Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! L-Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nose guy! What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they setting sail\Njust because the Navy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed that you were on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?! I'm still right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we fought together\Neven after our argument?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot... named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get me a lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who fought outstandingly\Nas that king of snipers, Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave up on me because I disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The stairs are broken! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Guys! No more worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:16:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp's coming, Luffy! Usopp's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Rejoice! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! It's a fine day today! Let's go fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is no time for that, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I've got good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not, when I'm back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind becoming your Vice Captain!\NWhat do you think? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're crying with joy over there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you are, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I can't go along with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to cause you trouble until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually\Nbelieved that joke I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been friends for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd say\Nsomething like that seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we said all sorts of things\Nto each other, we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let these little things go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Usopp's talking to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! I know you can hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really are trying to part with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy! It's not like everyone\Ncan live looking ahead like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave our wounded friend\Nhere and move on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that I can't keep\Nup with your monstrous strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need weak friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... you're the man\Nwho'll be king of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to go that high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, when I was about to sail out,\Nyou guys asked me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that's tying us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to travel together\Nwhen we have a difference of opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me say one last thing. You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'm going is my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you guys anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...leaving the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being bullheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm being pathetic.\NI know I said I was leaving the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... is there any chance\Nthat I can take that back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me join you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Grab my hand already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's finally on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna hurry up and get\Nthrough this cannonball attack
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that we can get on with our adventure, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Chopper. We finally have a bounty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I can't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50...? 50...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko, Gen-san, and everyone\Nin Cocoyashi Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they'll feel when they see this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wanted Posters Make It Around the World!\NCelebration in Their Hometowns
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Ship Moves Forward!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
